originalText.text: Dr Engel is by far my favorite doctor! She is extremely knowledgeable, professional and caring. She takes the time to listen and answer all of my questions. My husband and I have both been working with Dr Engel to lose weight and be healthier. With Dr Engels help we have both lost the weight that we needed to and are now living a healthier lifestyle. Dr Engel was extremely supportive during this really hard journey! She would listen to our concerns and struggles and would give us helpful ideas and food suggestions. Dr Engel is passionate about what she does and it shows. Thank you so much Dr Engel for all of your help and support!

originalText.text: Dr. Annelise Engel is a caring doctor.  She has been my doctor since 2005.  When we met, I had some medical issues.  I just obtained medical insurance and sought a primary care.  I choose Dr. Engel's name out of a book; best oick ever.  From teh first visit, she expressed her concern and took steps to get all of my past records inorder to make a complete diagnosis.  Without this I probably would be dead.  I also take my Mother to see her.  She probably would be dead.  I recommedn Dr. Engel to friends, family and colleagues.  All say the same, she is great.  Geraldine, her nurse is awesome.  A great doctor is worth gold.  Dr. Engel is a great doctor.
